# dimaGoHome2
gs 'stat'

if dimaGohomeday = daystart:
	'You come to a beautiful private home and rang the bell. You opened the door to a pretty blonde of about forty years, apparently the mother of Dimka. She looked at you and smiled "Dimka is not at home."'

	act 'Leave':gt 'gorodok'
elseif dimaGohomeday ! daystart:
	'You come to a beautiful private home and rang the bell. You opened the door to a pretty blonde of about forty years, apparently the mother of Dimka. She looked at you and smiled "You Dimka?" You nodded and mother of Dimka let you in the house.'

	act 'Go into the room Dimka':dimaGohomeday = daystart & gt 'dimaHome'
end

